column5: Hey guys, I've got a small bass/pike tourney on Baptiste this weekend.  I've never fished this lake before and I'm looking for some advice for this time of year.  Thanks in advance. Tim
I grew up fishing the lake, I do a trip every year with my dad and brother. . Find a map and PM me. I can prob give you a few of my fav spots
I fish that area heavily. PM me and I'd be happy to share some patterns.
